'''''The Day of My Wedding''''', ni filime ngufi ya [[Botswana|Botswana yo mu]] 2007 iyobowe na Thato Rantao Mwosa kandi yakozwe na Thato Rantao Mwosa nka SaBantu Productions<ref>https://frankensaurus.com/The_Day_of_My_Wedding</ref>.   Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Erickka Jones mu mwanya wa mbere hamwe na Souleymane Sy Savane na Audrey Aduama mu nshingano zunganira<ref>https://pwcenter.org/profile/thato-mwosa</ref>. 

Filime yafatiwe muri Boston no muri Massachusetts, muri [[Amerika]]<ref>https://warriorwomenbook.wordpress.com/2010/10/13/warrior-woman-thato-rantau-mwosa/</ref>. Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://allafrica.com/stories/200508250595.html</ref>. Iyi filime yagaragaye bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Roxbury, muri [[Amerika]] ku ya 4 Kanama 2007<ref>http://www.filmfatales.org/directors/thatomwosa</ref>.

